source_snippet: GRCop-42 (Copper-4at% Chromium-2at% Niobium Alloy)
GRCop-42 offers 5–8% increases in thermal conductivity and ductility in the hot isostatic press (HIP) condition over GRCop-84 while maintaining comparable mechanical strengths.
